name: In the Tickle of Warhol's Fruit - Issue #10
description:
We Collect the World - the photography issue
Art Zine focused on Hic et Nunc artists and writers featuring Damla Sahinbas, Roman Drits and Adi with a poem by Yasmin Senzii. Created by Wily Guys (@guyswily) and Maia Mellier (@maiamellier)
